Project Buxton

1. Check out from <http://svn3.cvsdude.com/BlackRadley/buxton/trunk>.

2. Run db:migrate to create the database.

3. The subdomain determines the CSS style so set up these aliases for localhost*:
	birmingham.localhost
	www.localhost
	buxton.local (for 27stars development)
	* This will be in /etc/hosts for Mac/Linux and C:\Windows\System32\Drivers\Etc\HOSTS for Windows

4. To receive a reminder email visit <http://www.localhost:3000/user> and enter your email address.